import React from "react"

function Skill(props) {
    console.log(props)
    const skills=[...props.language,props.role,props.level]
    console.log(skills)


    return (<React.Fragment>
        <button type="button" class="btn  skill-button my-2 me-2">{skills}</button>
        
    </React.Fragment>
    )
}

export default Skill
